reviews.review: this is a great redemption story for this franchise. after a pair of lackluster outings, this one brings back the glory of Star Wars. while choppy at times, this film does an admirable job of cramming an immense amount of lore and nostalgia into it's runtime.
An absolute triumph. Thank you to J.J. for completing the final chapter of the story of my life so perfectly. I couldn't have asked for more and can't stop thinking about it. Just brilliant.

Loved it!  This is coming  from someone who saw the original Star Wars 4 times at the theater in 1977 and has been obsessed with it for 42 years.  I don't understand why so many have to pick it apart.  It was exciting, entertaining, and it gave me all the feels that I get from watching Star Wars.  It was a very satisfying wrap of the saga!

This movie was AWESOME....Love it!!!!....JJ SAVED Star Wars from that last movie which was the worst Star Wars movie ever.....this one cleaned up that complete mess and gave Star Wars a GREAT ending to this trilogy.....thanks JJ FANTASTIC!!!!!....and the real test is yes I will buy this movie when it comes out....that movie before this one was the only Star Wars movie I saw one time and have zero desire to ever see it again...even when it's free to watch again on Netflix....just a waste of time.....this one however, I'll watch at least a few more times ....it was WONDERFUL thanks again JJ
I love the movie! its so worth watching! I don't mind going to see it again!!!!!!!
good action, keeps you engaged.  unless you are deep into the star wars world you won't mind some of the plot holes and unusual choices made in the movie

The movie surpassed my expectations; it has action; the plot was able to connect all the movie saga, make you laugh, and even can make you cry. The FXs and the sound were top.   I will see it twice.  I will repeat it in IMAX theater. Great movie,  people need to pay attention to the details.
Excellent. I don't get why all the reviews were so bad. This one came pretty close to being one of my favorites.
Really enjoyed the storyline. Tied up the trilogy very well. Might watch it again!
It delivered on what to expect. Graphics are really cool. The storyline could have been better, the dialogue was a bit to childish at some times. But what to expect from Disney.
